'''The Transport (Wales) Act 2006''' (c 5) is an [[Act of Parliament|Act]] of the [[Parliament of the United Kingdom]]. It was passed in response to a resolution approved by the [[National Assembly for Wales]] on 17 March 2004.<ref>Explanatory notes, [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2006/5/notes/division/2 paragraph 3]</ref>
==Section 12 - Commencement== [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2006/1403/contents/made The Transport (Wales) Act 2006 (Commencement) Order 2006] (S.I. 2006/1403 (W.140) (C.48)) was made under this section.
